{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/jtbd-lesson-2-the-jtbd-doesnt-change-the-product-we-hire-does/","result":{"data":{"post":{"id":"cG9zdDo2MDkx","excerpt":"<p>The second key lesson you might have already spotted in the example from Lesson 1: The JOB doesn’t change, The Product we hire does. Consider the previous JTBD, &#8220;sharing a &#8230; </p>\n<div><a href=\"/jtbd-lesson-2-the-jtbd-doesnt-change-the-product-we-hire-does/\" class=\"more-link\">Read More</a></div>\n","content":"\n<p>The second key lesson you might have already spotted in the example from <a href=\"/jtbd-lesson-1-focus-on-the-higher-purpose/\">Lesson 1</a>: The JOB doesn’t change, <strong>The Product we hire does</strong>. Consider the previous JTBD, &#8220;sharing a moment with others&#8221;&#8230;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Below is a (totally science fiction today) product from Magic Leap, an Augmented Reality startup working on overlaying 3D images on your reality.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1032\" height=\"718\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/blackswanfarming/images/f_auto,q_auto/w_1032,h_718/v1613032018/W/image-13/image-13.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6060\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/blackswanfarming/images/f_auto,q_auto/v1613032018/W/image-13/image-13.png 1032w, https://res.cloudinary.com/blackswanfarming/images/f_auto,q_auto/w_300,h_209,c_scale/v1613032018/W/image-13/image-13-300x209.png 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/blackswanfarming/images/f_auto,q_auto/w_1024,h_712,c_scale/v1613032018/W/image-13/image-13-1024x712.png 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/blackswanfarming/images/f_auto,q_auto/w_768,h_534,c_scale/v1613032018/W/image-13/image-13-768x534.png 768w, https://res.cloudinary.com/blackswanfarming/images/f_auto,q_auto/w_100,h_70,c_scale/v1613032018/W/image-13/image-13-100x70.png 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1032px) 100vw, 1032px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This was produced by Weta Workshop, so is basically CGI today, but imagine what adding <em>depth</em> to our digital images will do to shift the products we hire <em>again.</em> Apple in particular seems to be flexing it&#8217;s R&amp;D in this area, first with FaceID using depth to make sure it&#8217;s you who is accessing your phone. The latest iPad has a full on LiDAR camera on board. Both the hardware and software are underwhelming today, but what might happen as it gets better in many ways?</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1196\" height=\"728\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/blackswanfarming/images/f_auto,q_auto/w_1196,h_728/v1613032016/W/image-14/image-14.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6061\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/blackswanfarming/images/f_auto,q_auto/v1613032016/W/image-14/image-14.png 1196w, https://res.cloudinary.com/blackswanfarming/images/f_auto,q_auto/w_300,h_183,c_scale/v1613032016/W/image-14/image-14-300x183.png 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/blackswanfarming/images/f_auto,q_auto/w_1024,h_623,c_scale/v1613032016/W/image-14/image-14-1024x623.png 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/blackswanfarming/images/f_auto,q_auto/w_768,h_467,c_scale/v1613032016/W/image-14/image-14-768x467.png 768w, https://res.cloudinary.com/blackswanfarming/images/f_auto,q_auto/w_100,h_61,c_scale/v1613032016/W/image-14/image-14-100x61.png 100w, https://res.cloudinary.com/blackswanfarming/images/f_auto,q_auto/w_1170,h_712,c_scale/v1613032016/W/image-14/image-14-1170x712.png 1170w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1196px) 100vw, 1196px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Another possible &#8220;new product&#8221; that we might employ for this same JTBD is Virtual Reality, where using a headset you can be transported anywhere – so I could perhaps share with all of you what it’s like to get barrelled in Indonesia.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Of course, we’ve seen these shifts many, many times before. Consider how much the way we listen to recorded music has changed over the last 50 years:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1494\" height=\"1122\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/blackswanfarming/images/f_auto,q_auto/w_1494,h_1122/v1613032014/W/image-16/image-16.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6064\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/blackswanfarming/images/f_auto,q_auto/v1613032014/W/image-16/image-16.png 1494w, https://res.cloudinary.com/blackswanfarming/images/f_auto,q_auto/w_300,h_225,c_scale/v1613032014/W/image-16/image-16-300x225.png 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/blackswanfarming/images/f_auto,q_auto/w_1024,h_769,c_scale/v1613032014/W/image-16/image-16-1024x769.png 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/blackswanfarming/images/f_auto,q_auto/w_768,h_577,c_scale/v1613032014/W/image-16/image-16-768x577.png 768w, https://res.cloudinary.com/blackswanfarming/images/f_auto,q_auto/w_100,h_75,c_scale/v1613032014/W/image-16/image-16-100x75.png 100w, https://res.cloudinary.com/blackswanfarming/images/f_auto,q_auto/w_1170,h_879,c_scale/v1613032014/W/image-16/image-16-1170x879.png 1170w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1494px) 100vw, 1494px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Vinyl to cassettes, to CDs, to MP3, to various forms of streaming today. Again: the job has stayed largely the same, but we have switched the products we hire for this job many times.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The lesson here is to really, really consider alternatives. Your product may be unique, but the underlying JTBD is not. Don’t be lazy or closed-minded here. If you really<strong> </strong>can’t identify an alternative, then there’s a good chance that you’re solving a problem that no one has!</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\" />\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Want to learn more? Here&#8217;s 5 lessons you can get from Jobs to be Done (JTBD):</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The intro: <a href=\"/jtbd-jobs-to-be-done-an-intro/\">JTBD (Jobs to be Done) – An Intro</a></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><a href=\"/jtbd-lesson-1-focus-on-the-higher-purpose/\">JTBD Lesson #1: Focus on the higher purpose</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>JTBD Lesson #2: The JTBD doesn’t change. The product we hire does.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>JTBD Lesson #3: Beware of Overserving</p>\n\n\n\n<p>JTBD Lesson #4: Segment by JTBD</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<p>(Above will get updated with links as they are published!)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Previous Posts on Jobs to be Done:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"/health-tracking-jobs-to-be-done/\">Health Tracking Jobs to be Done</a></p>\n</div></div>\n","title":"JTBD Lesson #2: The Job to be Done doesn’t change.","date":"May 16, 2020","featuredImage":{"node":{"altText":"","localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='400'%20height='300'%20viewBox='0%200%20400%20300'%20preserveAspectRatio='none'%3e%3cpath%20d='M219%2042l-2%205c0%202-1%203-3%200l1%204-3-3c-4-4-9-7-12-7l2%201c3%202%207%207%2010%2012l2%204-5-1c-6-1-8-1-12%201l-4%202-1%2012v22c1%2010%201%2011-1%2013h-4c-1-1-4-3-7-3-4-2-5-2-6-7-2-4-2-6-1-7v-7c0-8-2-8-2-2v5l-1-4c-1-6-3-6-3%200%200%204%200%205%202%205%203%200%203%202%202%204v15c-4%207%200%2017%205%2017l4%203c3%202%204%202%2011%200%202%200%202%200%202%204v4l16%205%2017%205V67l4-1c4-2%204-4%201-4s-3-1-3-8c-2-13-5-18-9-12M15%2082c0%2030%200%2034%201%2033l6-1%203%201-5%203c-5%203-5%204-5%208l1%204c2%200%206-6%205-7l2-1c3%201%206%200%208-2s2-2%203%200%200%204-4%209l-5%206h15l4-8c3-7%205-8%209-5%202%202%204-2%202-5-3-4-3-4%201-4%203%200%203%200%202%204l-1%204-1%203v7l-1%204h14v-8l-1-7%202%201c3%202%207%203%207%201l-1-1-2-3-2-4%202-1%203%204%201%203%204-4c4-5%205-6%202-6v-8c0-3%201-4%203-5%203-1%205%201%205%203l3%203c3%202%203%202%201%202l-3-1-1-1c-2%200-1%208%201%2011l7%207%205%207c0%202%201%201%205-2%2025-17%2025-51%201-69-5-4-6-5-6-7%200-3%200-3-3-3l-3%201-1%203-2%202-2%201-2%201-1%201c-1-1-2%200-3%201%200%202-1%203-5%202-7%200-9%201-10%204l-2%203v5c1%201%201%201-1%201-